N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 13 ยง 201.1 - Scope of part

State Regulations

This Part shall govern the conduct of hearings held by the Bureau of Investor

Protection and Securities of the Department of Law pursuant to chapter 730, Laws of 1980, the New York Franchise Sales Act, and as amended from time
to time. Notes
